{"tid":295333,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(擺明係reference狗) 安信果張WEWA咭真係幾抵屌","createTime":"2017-06-23T16:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T23:41:58.000Z","uid":61153,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"454af7fd3d1b9647b8528d507fa86374bafb6427","tid":295333,"uid":61153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"簽夠4舊水就可以抽一次獎 d獎仲要幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/232411_fb93fe89014c1144b626b74930db4cb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F232411_fb93fe89014c1144b626b74930db4cb5.jpg&h=a3a2462c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/232413_84b6b4eddd96bd3d558e6cad94fc423d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F232413_84b6b4eddd96bd3d558e6cad94fc423d.jpg&h=4521dd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次簽咭都好似有個9折咁 又回贈又哈根大師券 好鐘意食哈根大師 張現金券唔岩用仲可以轉返做現金回贈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我岩岩先出卡冇乜抽到獎 仲有d咩可以拎到可以睇呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wewacard.com/wewa_luckydraw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wewacard.com%2Fwewa_luckydraw%2F&d=133p1LRAIpg7kyuPimlQsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f5612a7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wewacard.com/wewa_luckydraw/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外就係去旅行 睇戲 唱k 去op同迪迪尼 有4%回贈 你買張5000蚊機票 已經袋返兩舊水 你話爽唔爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n報個旅行團都一樣有得回贈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我講咁多都係想大家睇完有興趣出咭既話 可以用下面條link出 幫家境清貧既小弟找下咭數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都多兩舊水回贈洗 我呢啲reference打手死全家又有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.primecredit.com/happy1m/?r=OOAUIS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.primecredit.com%2Fhappy1m%2F%3Fr%3DOOAUIS&d=133p1LRAIpg7kyuPimlQsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b0cbce0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.primecredit.com/happy1m/?r=OOAUIS</a>"},{"pid":"99d01dfa3b5ccb846f3ba0324ec8e35c561d41df","tid":295333,"uid":61153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd732bf567de7fc4da10fe3159189a0f4c814673","tid":295333,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"自己睇"},{"pid":"a770276f578348529679723a99fad0b2823b7464","tid":295333,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/001807_7522357527c8040e72d4ccbfb01b39ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F001807_7522357527c8040e72d4ccbfb01b39ea.jpg&h=c72aeb13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d90a82db6a75c6d44449cb35fe5bac3816cabc1","tid":295333,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"安信 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdda0fa41f7a1f7bfa77ce3035eedcbf4a55484","tid":295333,"uid":71766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安信 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1f579dc4153c66c4450b6b2ce7865c87fcd3a5","tid":295333,"uid":61153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T18:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/001807_7522357527c8040e72d4ccbfb01b39ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-